  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multi scrolling mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seamlessly switching between side scroll, top-down, 3d shooter from behind and cut-scene. No camera cut during stage run. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Appearance</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No story narration. The story is abstract.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some parts of game are refered from other Touhou Project derivative works. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters are in alternate sexy costume<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/1926031004e3d76c508b8ab71d366966.avif?t=1767536362\" width=720 height=540 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keyboard control (default)</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow keys : Move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >z : Shoot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >x : Use bomb</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >c : Use special skill</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left shift : Slowdown movement and aim at enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space bar : turn</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >escape : pause game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can set key config as you want in the option menu.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Playable characters</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hakurei Reimu <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/6589eb644a835f8de18529bf54669262.avif?t=1767536362\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kirisame Marisa <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/9ff820ccca98549555231665b8baf321.avif?t=1767536362\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Izayoi Sakuya <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/a8aadaea0dfaa39119a03cfd61b4332d.avif?t=1767536362\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Miscellaneous game play features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 stages for main game + 1 extra stage.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 difficulties. Easy, Normal and Hard.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Screen resolution setting. 3840x2160, 3200x1800, 2560x1440, 1920x1080, 1280x720, 640x360. Choose which ever suitable for your machine. The game has better performance with a lower resolution. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cel-shade and Hitbox style setting. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hp and Mp regenerate.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/cd9c9814aed41ff3d79b40f2078f720e.avif?t=1767536362\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlimited continue. When player dies, player can continue at any unlocked checkpoint. If player use continue, the remaining hp is set to small amount.  No bad ending even a player use continue. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill enemies in close range to get more bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill enemies consecutively to get more chain bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partially Japanese and Chinese translation. (Tutorial and UI)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Save game location</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >C:UsersusernameAppDataLocalTHMSS2</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multi scrolling mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seamlessly switching between side scroll, top-down, 3d shooter from behind and cut-scene. No camera cut during stage run. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Appearance</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No story narration. The story is abstract.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some parts of game are refered from other Touhou Project derivative works. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters are in alternate sexy costume<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/1926031004e3d76c508b8ab71d366966.avif?t=1767536362\" width=720 height=540 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keyboard control (default)</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow keys : Move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >z : Shoot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >x : Use bomb</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >c : Use special skill</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left shift : Slowdown movement and aim at enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space bar : turn</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >escape : pause game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can set key config as you want in the option menu.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Playable characters</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hakurei Reimu <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/6589eb644a835f8de18529bf54669262.avif?t=1767536362\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kirisame Marisa <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/9ff820ccca98549555231665b8baf321.avif?t=1767536362\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Izayoi Sakuya <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/a8aadaea0dfaa39119a03cfd61b4332d.avif?t=1767536362\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Miscellaneous game play features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 stages for main game + 1 extra stage.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 difficulties. Easy, Normal and Hard.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Screen resolution setting. 3840x2160, 3200x1800, 2560x1440, 1920x1080, 1280x720, 640x360. Choose which ever suitable for your machine. The game has better performance with a lower resolution. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cel-shade and Hitbox style setting. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hp and Mp regenerate.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480040/extras/cd9c9814aed41ff3d79b40f2078f720e.avif?t=1767536362\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlimited continue. When player dies, player can continue at any unlocked checkpoint. If player use continue, the remaining hp is set to small amount.  No bad ending even a player use continue. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill enemies in close range to get more bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill enemies consecutively to get more chain bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partially Japanese and Chinese translation. (Tutorial and UI)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Save game location</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >C:UsersusernameAppDataLocalTHMSS2</p>",
